  26:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  27:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                        ##### SDMMC peripheral features #####
  28:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  29:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     [..] The SD/SDMMC MMC card host interface (SDMMC) provides an interface between the AHB
  30:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          peripheral bus and MultiMedia cards (MMCs), SD memory cards, SDMMC cards and CE-ATA
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccEOXLVK.s 			page 2


  31:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          devices.
  32:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  33:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     [..] The SDMMC features include the following:
  34:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Full compliance with MultiMediaCard System Specification Version 4.51. Card support
  35:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****              for three different databus modes: 1-bit (default), 4-bit and 8-bit.
  36:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Full compatibility with previous versions of MultiMediaCards (backward compatibility).
  37:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Full compliance with SD memory card specifications version 4.1.
  38:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****              (SDR104 SDMMC_CK speed limited to maximum allowed IO speed, SPI mode and
  39:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****               UHS-II mode not supported).
  40:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Full compliance with SDIO card specification version 4.0. Card support
  41:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****              for two different databus modes: 1-bit (default) and 4-bit.
  42:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****              (SDR104 SDMMC_CK speed limited to maximum allowed IO speed, SPI mode and
  43:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****               UHS-II mode not supported).
  44:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Data transfer up to 208 Mbyte/s for the 8 bit mode. (depending maximum allowed IO spee
  45:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****          (+) Data and command output enable signals to control external bidirectional drivers
  46:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  47:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                            ##### How to use this driver #####
  48:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****   ==============================================================================
  49:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     [..]
  50:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       This driver is a considered as a driver of service for external devices drivers
  51:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       that interfaces with the SDMMC peripheral.
  52:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       According to the device used (SD card/ MMC card / SDMMC card ...), a set of APIs
  53:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       is used in the device's driver to perform SDMMC operations and functionalities.
  54:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  55:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       This driver is almost transparent for the final user, it is only used to implement other
  56:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       functionalities of the external device.
  57:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  58:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     [..]
  59:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) The SDMMC clock (SDMMCCLK = 48 MHz) is coming from a specific output (MSI, PLLUSB1CLK,
  60:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           PLLUSB2CLK). Before start working with SDMMC peripheral make sure that the
  61:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           PLL is well configured.
  62:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           The SDMMC peripheral uses two clock signals:
  63:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           (++) SDMMC adapter clock (SDMMCCLK = 48 MHz)
  64:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           (++) APB2 bus clock (PCLK2)
  65:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  66:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           -@@- PCLK2 and SDMMC_CK clock frequencies must respect the following condition:
  67:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                Frequency(PCLK2) >= (3 / 8 x Frequency(SDMMC_CK)) for STM32L496xG and STM32L4A6xG
  68:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                Frequency(PCLK2) >= (3 / 4 x Frequency(SDMMC_CK)) otherwise
  69:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  70:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) Enable/Disable peripheral clock using RCC peripheral macros related to SDMMC
  71:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           peripheral.
  72:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  73:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) Enable the Power ON State using the SDMMC_PowerState_ON(SDMMCx)
  74:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           function and disable it using the function SDMMC_PowerState_OFF(SDMMCx).
  75:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  76:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) Enable/Disable the clock using the __SDMMC_ENABLE()/__SDMMC_DISABLE() macros.
  77:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  78:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) Enable/Disable the peripheral interrupts using the macros __SDMMC_ENABLE_IT(hSDMMC, IT)
  79:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           and __SDMMC_DISABLE_IT(hSDMMC, IT) if you need to use interrupt mode.
  80:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  81:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) When using the DMA mode
  82:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           (++) On STM32L4Rx/STM32L4Sxx devices
  83:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Configure the IDMA mode (Single buffer or double)
  84:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Configure the buffer address
  85:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Configure Data Path State Machine
  86:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           (++) On other devices
  87:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Configure the DMA in the MSP layer of the external device
ARM GAS  /tmp/ccEOXLVK.s 			page 3


  88:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Active the needed channel Request 
  89:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                (+++) Enable the DMA using __SDMMC_DMA_ENABLE() macro or Disable it using the macro
  90:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****                      __SDMMC_DMA_DISABLE().
  91:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
  92:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) To control the CPSM (Command Path State Machine) and send
  93:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           commands to the card use the SDMMC_SendCommand(SDMMCx),
  94:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           SDMMC_GetCommandResponse() and SDMMC_GetResponse() functions. First, user has
  95:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           to fill the command structure (pointer to SDMMC_CmdInitTypeDef) according
  96:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           to the selected command to be sent.
  97:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           The parameters that should be filled are:
  98:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Command Argument
  99:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Command Index
 100:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Command Response type
 101:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Command Wait
 102:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) CPSM Status (Enable or Disable).
 103:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
 104:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           -@@- To check if the command is well received, read the SDMMC_CMDRESP
 105:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****               register using the SDMMC_GetCommandResponse().
 106:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****               The SDMMC responses registers (SDMMC_RESP1 to SDMMC_RESP2), use the
 107:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****               SDMMC_GetResponse() function.
 108:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
 109:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (+) To control the DPSM (Data Path State Machine) and send/receive
 110:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            data to/from the card use the SDMMC_DataConfig(), SDMMC_GetDataCounter(),
 111:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           SDMMC_ReadFIFO(), SDMMC_WriteFIFO() and SDMMC_GetFIFOCount() functions.
 112:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c **** 
 113:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     *** Read Operations ***
 114:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     =======================
 115:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****     [..]
 116:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****       (#) First, user has to fill the data structure (pointer to
 117:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           SDMMC_DataInitTypeDef) according to the selected data type to be received.
 118:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****           The parameters that should be filled are:
 119:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Data TimeOut
 120:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Data Length
 121:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Data Block size
 122:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Data Transfer direction: should be from card (To SDMMC)
 123:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) Data Transfer mode
 124:Drivers/STM32L4xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32l4xx_ll_sdmmc.c ****            (++) DPSM Status (Enable or Disable)
